<template><h1 id="基础应用" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#基础应用" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 基础应用</h1>
<h2 id="创建一个-hello-world-程序" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#创建一个-hello-world-程序" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 创建一个 Hello World 程序</h2>
<p>新建一个控制台项目，在 main.aardio 输入以下代码，点击 运行(F5) 程序</p>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">//引入 console 库</span>
<span class="token keyword">import</span> console<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token comment">//打印 Hello World</span>
console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Hello World"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token comment">//暂停，按任意键退出</span>
console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">pause</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br></div></div><h2 id="编译-执行" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#编译-执行" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 编译 &amp; 执行</h2>
<p>点击 发布(F7) 按钮生成EXE文件</p>
<p>运行exe文件</p>
</template>
